Canyon Crossroads
Players: 2–4
Type: Skirmish / Ring Hero Compatible

Map Description
Four paths meet between cliffs and narrow chasms.
Springs fill the craters at the center of the land.
Hold the heart or be flanked from every side.
Watch out for those monsters—find Gollum and claim the ring!

Lore – Veins of the Earth
Once a sacred site where ancient druids drew power from the land.
Erosion has carved deep scars through its heart, revealing its lifeblood—water and stone.
Those who command the crossroads now awaken echoes of forgotten power.